{"tid":386721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人聽過曼德拉效應 人類真係返到過去？","createTime":"2017-09-04T05:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T19:26:48.000Z","uid":86453,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1da33cf9d0ff9eab5fb4ad7fe9f0a5d67ba19e21","tid":386721,"uid":86453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"睇完真係覺得好不可思議！仲有好多例子都好似層層咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1Z5lu-nE-a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1Z5lu-nE-a8&d=ZHrH1%2FwvHXf6jfny9QUxD8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ac6e1c44\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1Z5lu-nE-a8</a>"},{"pid":"255a53d5afcf4040eeabda308b7c75747965e00c","tid":386721,"uid":128593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:11:34.000Z","msg":"羅馬數字中，IIII和IV都可以表示4。<br />\n之所以大多用IIII而不是用IV，可能有以下這些原因：<br />\n1.\t早期的一些大鐘在建造的那個年代，人們普遍喜歡用IIII而非IV。<br />\n2.\t避諱羅馬神Jupiter（拉丁文 IVPPITER）<br />\n3.\t法國路易十四Louis XIV更喜歡IIII<br />\n4.\tIV和VI在錶盤上都是上下顛倒的，容易被兒童混淆。<br />\n5.\tIIII和另一側同一位置的VIII都有4個字元，更具對稱美。<br />\n6.\t錶盤上前4個小時含有I，後四個含有V，最後四個含有X，更具美感。<br />\n7.\t用IIII的話，鐘錶製造者只需要4個VIIIIIX的模組就可以分割出所需的12個字元。<br />\n8.\t（來自wikipedia）"},{"pid":"3bb6e459e6ac01c7c014a839f54dd3336e49dbb8","tid":386721,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:12:49.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"d4fba2821c680fa76d520989dde4d808a1a28289","tid":386721,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羅馬數字中，IIII和IV都可以表示4。<br />\n之所以大多用IIII而不是用IV，可能有以下這些原因：<br />\n1.\t早期的一些大鐘在建造的那個年代，人們普遍喜歡用IIII而非IV。<br />\n2.\t避諱羅馬神Jupiter（拉丁文 IVPPITER）<br />\n3.\t法國路易十四Louis XIV更喜歡IIII<br />\n4.\tIV和VI在錶盤上都是上下顛倒的，容易被兒童混淆。<br />\n5.\tIIII和另一側同一位置的VIII都有4個字元，更具對稱美。<br />\n6.\t錶盤上前4個小時含有I，後四個含有V，最後四個含有X，更具美感。<br />\n7.\t用IIII的話，鐘錶製造者只需要4個VIIIIIX的模組就可以分割出所需的12個字元。<br />\n8.\t（來自wikipedia）</blockquote><br />\n9.樓主係弱智"},{"pid":"4d5ed5c6c1072ac250591656b6f7182b8b4fd783","tid":386721,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"所有野都可以解釋到<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4sMQNQUcogM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4sMQNQUcogM&d=ZHrH1%2FwvHXf6jfny9QUxD8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4e188e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4sMQNQUcogM</a>"},{"pid":"689d5c21fccc480607671648935c558c189465a3","tid":386721,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>羅馬數字中，IIII和IV都可以表示4。<br />\n之所以大多用IIII而不是用IV，可能有以下這些原因：<br />\n1.\t早期的一些大鐘在建造的那個年代，人們普遍喜歡用IIII而非IV。<br />\n2.\t避諱羅馬神Jupiter（拉丁文 IVPPITER）<br />\n3.\t法國路易十四Louis XIV更喜歡IIII<br />\n4.\tIV和VI在錶盤上都是上下顛倒的，容易被兒童混淆。<br />\n5.\tIIII和另一側同一位置的VIII都有4個字元，更具對稱美。<br />\n6.\t錶盤上前4個小時含有I，後四個含有V，最後四個含有X，更具美感。<br />\n7.\t用IIII的話，鐘錶製造者只需要4個VIIIIIX的模組就可以分割出所需的12個字元。<br />\n8.\t（來自wikipedia）</blockquote><br />\n9.樓主係弱智</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1979e183c5ff6ead5e07ab86aec4c0a36ead91f0","tid":386721,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"On9仔先信"},{"pid":"ba4c8ec38547b4bd67799ec9433e4472200c3659","tid":386721,"uid":56702,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"又share錫安邪教啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43c2c1fe6988f484777a36daecd270925c14a51","tid":386721,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:16:25.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"bb471d1e4f1363151715fbbecf049f166cb883c6","tid":386721,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:11:22.000Z","msg":"ON撚柒鳩，<br /